result.name: 炑八韓烤 (荃新天地店)

reviews.text: 地方舒適，兩三個朋友或一大班人都適合，食物ok, 平日有簡單套餐，附加小食。還有任食的泡菜蛋，粟米芝士，兩個女仔已食得好飽。又可以談心。
地方寬敞，好舒適。食物跟其他韓燒大同小異。醬油蟹不似其他韓燒，醬料不過份的咸。加分。
這間的招呼不錯, 落單後食物好快就到, 侍應生見你的配菜食完, 會主動問加不加配菜(例如泡菜, 酸羅白等), 食材也新鮮
服務和食品滿意,今次等四次仍有水準
質量ok，價格抵，員工友善，會再去！

reviews.text: I thought this restaurant was pretty good. Admittedly, I'm a huge fan of Korean BBQ, so this place already earned my favour from the start. However, compared to other similar restaurants, the food quality is above average and the customer service is fantastic. For the price, you also get pretty generous portions as well. I was pretty satisfied with my dining experience here, and would probably visit here again.

The food here is reasonably priced and of good quality. The standout thing for us was the service - the staff were knowledgeable and enthusiastic, and helped us cook and cut our food. On the side of the barbecue plate they also cooked egg and kimchi, as well as cheese and corn, both of which are very tasty. Worth a visit!
reasonable price and good taste
